OL,7,FThe mother of a man who took his own
OL,8,Flife while on unescorted leave from a
OL,9,Fmental health hospital says she will
OL,10,Fnever get over the death of her only
OL,11,Fchild.
OL,13,FTy Channce was under the care of the
OL,14,FTees, Esk and Wear Valleys NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust (TEWV) at Roseberry
OL,16,FPark Hospital, in Middlesbrough, when
OL,17,Fhe was let out alone for the first
OL,18,Ftime in nine months in April 2021.
OL,20,FJust hours later, the 20-year-old was
OL,21,Ffound dead in nearby woodland.
