OL,7,FAn inquest last week found there had
OL,8,Fhad being a number of failings by TEWV
OL,9,Fwhich contributed to his death.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, his mother
OL,12,FCheryl Allan said: "It's absolutely
OL,13,Fbroken us all, we're never going to
OL,14,Fget over the loss of Ty, he was so
OL,15,Floved.
OL,17,F"To put him into somebody else's hands
OL,18,Fand never get him back has absolutely
OL,19,Fbroken our family apart."
