OL,7,FTy was sectioned under the mental
OL,8,Fhealth act in 2018, at the age of 18.
OL,10,FHe was struggling with psychosis
OL,11,Fcaused by his schizophrenia and
OL,12,Fadmitted to Roseberry Park Hospital.
OL,14,FMs Allan said: "Even though he was in
OL,15,Fthere to get better I feel like he'd
OL,16,Fbeen taken away from me.
OL,18,F"We thought he was going in there to
OL,19,Fget the best of the help."
