OL,7,FMs Allan said that over time her son's
OL,8,Fcondition in hospital deteriorated,
OL,9,Fsomething she said she raised concerns
OL,10,Fabout "on a regular basis".
OL,12,FOn 28 April 2021, Ty requested, and
OL,13,Fwas granted, two hours of unescorted
OL,14,Fcommunity leave off the hospital
OL,15,Fgrounds.
OL,17,FIt was the first time in nine months
OL,18,Fhe had been granted unescorted leave
OL,19,Fdue to lockdown restrictions.
