OL,7,FHe left the hospital at 3:30pm with
OL,8,F#60, which he had asked for, to go to
OL,9,Fa cafe.
OL,11,FHe did not return to the hospital and
OL,12,Fwas found dead in woods near Nunthorpe
OL,13,Fat 6:29pm the same day.
OL,15,FMrs Allan said the loss of her son
OL,16,Fsaid has "torn her family apart".
OL,18,FShe added: "We're filled with a hole
OL,19,Fin our hearts that will never be
OL,20,Ffilled again."
