OL,7,FIn response to the findings of the
OL,8,Finquest into Ty's death, the trust's
OL,9,Fchief nurse Beverley Murphy said: "We
OL,10,Funderstand how difficult a coroner
OL,11,Fhearing can be, and our thoughts are
OL,12,Fwith Ty's family during this difficult
OL,13,Ftime. We are sincerely sorry for their
OL,14,Floss.
OL,16,F"We reviewed Ty's care and have made
OL,17,Fseveral improvements, including the
OL,18,Fintroduction of new medication
OL,19,Fpractices to more robustly monitor
OL,20,Fself-administered medication.
