OL,7,F"We will act on the inquest findings
OL,8,Fand continue to improve so that we can
OL,9,Fprovide the best care possible."
OL,11,FMs Allan said she cannot accept the
OL,12,Ftrust's apology and that changes now
OL,13,Fneed to be made to ensure that this
OL,14,Fdoesn't happen again.
OL,16,F"I can't stress enough that these
OL,17,Ffailings need to stop," she said.
